Package hu.akarnokd.rxjava2.joins

Utility methods for join patterns (more generic way than combineLatest) via JoinObservable wrapper and the and/then/when vocabulary; a port of the RxJavaJoins library.

Utility methods for join patterns (more generic way than combineLatest) via JoinObservable wrapper and the and/then/when vocabulary; a port of the RxJavaJoins library.
